  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC278">
        <l>oppil pōliyu mapporuṭ ṭākum.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/168/mode/1up">168</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/169/mode/1up">169</ref>.</p>
  <p>
ic cūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēl iṭaic col eḻuvakaiya eṉṟu niṟuttavaṟṟuḷ oppilpōli eṉṉum iṭaiccol uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
</p>
<p>
oppilpōli yāvatu, oppillātavaḻi oppitta vācakam paṭa varuvatu eṉpatu.
</p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC278-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘maṅkalam eṉpatōr ūruṇṭupōlum maḻanāṭṭuḷ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa oppillātavaḻip pōlum eṉṉum iṭaic col vantavāṟu. (30)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n219/mode/1up">216</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i - ḷ. oppumaiyuṇarttāta pōliccollum āṅkaveṉpatupōla uraiyacaiyām. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m. 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC278-Cena-cit1">
        <l>maṅkalameṉpatōrūruṇṭupōlum</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
        pōlum pōlvatu eṉṉuntoṭakkattup palavāypāṭuntaḻuvutaṟkup pōliyeṉṟār.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC278-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘neruppaḻaṟ cērntakkā ṉeypōl vatūum’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉpatumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
acainilaiyum poruḷ kuṟittallatu nillāmaiyiṉ apporuṭṭākumeṉṟār.	(30)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/302/mode/1up">302</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/303/mode/1up">303</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        oppil pōli
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>oppil pōliyu mapporuṭ ṭākum.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
        (i-ḷ.) oppil pōliyu mapporuṭṭākum — oṉṟaṟ koṉ ṟokku meṉṉum poruḷ taṉkaṇiṉṟi varum pōliyeṉṉuñ collum akkaṭṭuraik kaṇṇē yacaitta nilaiyākiya poruḷai yuṭaittāy varumeṉṟa vāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
apporuṭ ṭeṉavē yāṅkavum poru ṭarutal peṟṟām.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m.)
      </p>
     <lg xml:id="TolC278-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘maṅkala meṉpatō rūruṇṭu pōlum’</l>
     </lg>
     <lg xml:id="TolC278-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘neruppaḻaṟ cērntakkā ṉeypōl vatūum’</l>
        <l>‘erippaccuṭ ṭevvanō yākkum.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉappōlu meṉṉu miṭaicco lūraiyum neyyaiyum puṉaintu niṉṟavāṟu kāṇka.  <num xml:lang="en">(30)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n186/mode/1up">179</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
        i-ḷ: ― oppuk kuṟiyāta pōl eṉṉum collum uraiyacaiyām. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m:― 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC278-Tey-cit1">
        <l>avar vantār pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        itaṉuḷ vantār eṉat tuṇintavaḻi varutaliṉ, acainilaiyāyiṟṟu.	[29]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
